nodes.text: Moxie Freemaker was a female human that was part of the Freemaker family.

Moxie Freemaker was first mentioned in the canon 2018 reference book Star Wars: Droidography. Later in 2018, she first appeared in "The Power at Jakku," an episode of the non-canon animated show LEGO Star Wars: All-Stars. Moxie was depicted as the daughter of Zander Freemaker and the niece of Rowan Freemaker and New Republic Senator Kordi Freemaker.
